{"id":462,"ayahs":[{"number":32,"arabic":"۞ فَمَنْ أَظْلَمُ مِمَّن كَذَبَ عَلَى ٱللَّهِ وَكَذَّبَ بِٱلصِّدْقِ إِذْ جَآءَهُۥٓ ۚ أَلَيْسَ فِى جَهَنَّمَ مَثْوًۭى لِّلْكَٰفِرِينَ","translation":"And who could be more wicked than he who invents lies about God? and gives the lie to the truth as soon as it has been placed before him? Is not hell the [proper] abode for all who deny the truth?","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4090.mp3","surahId":39,"words":[{"id":34579,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ فَمَنْ","translation":"অতঃপর কে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_032_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34580,"position":2,"arabic":"أَظْلَمُ","translation":"বড় সীমালঙ্ঘনকারী (হতে পারে)","audioUrl":"wbw/039_032_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34581,"position":3,"arabic":"مِمَّن","translation":"(তার) চেয়ে যে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_032_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34582,"position":4,"arabic":"كَذَبَ","translation":"মিথ্যা বলে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_032_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34583,"position":5,"arabic":"عَلَى","translation":"সম্পর্কে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_032_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34584,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_032_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34585,"position":7,"arabic":"وَكَذَّبَ","translation":"ও প্রত্যাখ্যান করে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_032_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34586,"position":8,"arabic":"بِٱلصِّدْقِ","translation":"পরম সত্যকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_032_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34587,"position":9,"arabic":"إِذْ","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/039_032_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34588,"position":10,"arabic":"جَآءَهُۥٓ ۚ","translation":"তার কাছে এসেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_032_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34590,"position":11,"arabic":"أَلَيْسَ","translation":"নয় কি","audioUrl":"wbw/039_032_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34591,"position":12,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_032_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34592,"position":13,"arabic":"جَهَنَّمَ","translation":"জাহান্নামের","audioUrl":"wbw/039_032_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34593,"position":14,"arabic":"مَثْوًۭى","translation":"আবাসস্থল","audioUrl":"wbw/039_032_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34594,"position":15,"arabic":"لِّلْكَـٰفِرِينَ","translation":"(এমন সব) কাফেরদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_032_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34595,"position":16,"arabic":"٣٢","translation":"(৩২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":33,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِى جَآءَ بِٱلصِّدْقِ وَصَدَّقَ بِهِۦٓ ۙ أُو۟لَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلْمُتَّقُونَ","translation":"But he who brings the truth, and he who wholeheartedly accepts it as true - it is they, they, who are [truly] conscious of Him!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4091.mp3","surahId":39,"words":[{"id":35180,"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِى","translation":"এবং যে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_033_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":35181,"position":2,"arabic":"جَآءَ","translation":"এসেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_033_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":35182,"position":3,"arabic":"بِٱلصِّدْقِ","translation":"পরম সত্যসহ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_033_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":35183,"position":4,"arabic":"وَصَدَّقَ","translation":"এবং (যারা) সত্য বলে মেনে নিয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_033_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":35184,"position":5,"arabic":"بِهِۦٓ ۙ","translation":"তাঁকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_033_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":35186,"position":6,"arabic":"أُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ","translation":"ঐসব লোক","audioUrl":"wbw/039_033_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":35187,"position":7,"arabic":"هُمُ","translation":"তারাই","audioUrl":"wbw/039_033_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":35188,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْمُتَّقُونَ","translation":"মুত্তাকী","audioUrl":"wbw/039_033_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":35189,"position":9,"arabic":"٣٣","translation":"(৩৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":34,"arabic":"لَهُم مَّا يَشَآءُونَ عِندَ رَبِّهِمْ ۚ ذَٰلِكَ جَزَآءُ ٱلْمُحْسِنِينَ","translation":"All that they have ever yearned for awaits them with their Sustainer: such will be the reward of the doers of good.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4092.mp3","surahId":39,"words":[{"id":36101,"position":1,"arabic":"لَهُم","translation":"তাদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_034_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36102,"position":2,"arabic":"مَّا","translation":"(থাকবে) যা","audioUrl":"wbw/039_034_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36103,"position":3,"arabic":"يَشَآءُونَ","translation":"তারা ইচ্ছে করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_034_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36104,"position":4,"arabic":"عِندَ","translation":"কাছে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_034_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36105,"position":5,"arabic":"رَبِّهِمْ ۚ","translation":"তাদের রবের","audioUrl":"wbw/039_034_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36107,"position":6,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এটা","audioUrl":"wbw/039_034_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36108,"position":7,"arabic":"جَزَآءُ","translation":"পুরস্কার","audioUrl":"wbw/039_034_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36109,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْمُحْسِنِينَ","translation":"সৎকর্মপরায়ণদের","audioUrl":"wbw/039_034_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36110,"position":9,"arabic":"٣٤","translation":"(৩৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":35,"arabic":"لِيُكَفِّرَ ٱللَّهُ عَنْهُمْ أَسْوَأَ ٱلَّذِى عَمِلُوا۟ وَيَجْزِيَهُمْ أَجْرَهُم بِأَحْسَنِ ٱلَّذِى كَانُوا۟ يَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"And to this end, God will efface from their record the worst that they ever did, and give them their reward in accordance with the best that they were doing [in life].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4093.mp3","surahId":39,"words":[{"id":36885,"position":1,"arabic":"لِيُكَفِّرَ","translation":"মোচন করেন যেন","audioUrl":"wbw/039_035_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36886,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_035_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36887,"position":3,"arabic":"عَنْهُمْ","translation":"তাদের থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_035_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36888,"position":4,"arabic":"أَسْوَأَ","translation":"মন্দকাজ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_035_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36889,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/039_035_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36890,"position":6,"arabic":"عَمِلُوا۟","translation":"তারা কাজ করেছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/039_035_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36891,"position":7,"arabic":"وَيَجْزِيَهُمْ","translation":"এবং তাদের প্রতিফল দেন (যেন)","audioUrl":"wbw/039_035_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36892,"position":8,"arabic":"أَجْرَهُم","translation":"পুরস্কার তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/039_035_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36893,"position":9,"arabic":"بِأَحْسَنِ","translation":"উত্তমভাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_035_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36894,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"(ঐ বিষয়ের) যা","audioUrl":"wbw/039_035_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36895,"position":11,"arabic":"كَانُوا۟","translation":"তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/039_035_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36896,"position":12,"arabic":"يَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"কাজ করেছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/039_035_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":36897,"position":13,"arabic":"٣٥","translation":"(৩৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":36,"arabic":"أَلَيْسَ ٱللَّهُ بِكَافٍ عَبْدَهُۥ ۖ وَيُخَوِّفُونَكَ بِٱلَّذِينَ مِن دُونِهِۦ ۚ وَمَن يُضْلِلِ ٱللَّهُ فَمَا لَهُۥ مِنْ هَادٍۢ","translation":"IS NOT God enough for His servant? And yet, they would frighten thee with those [imaginary divine powers which they worship] beside Him! But he whom God lets go astray can never find any guide,","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4094.mp3","surahId":39,"words":[{"id":37739,"position":1,"arabic":"أَلَيْسَ","translation":"কি নন","audioUrl":"wbw/039_036_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37740,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_036_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37741,"position":3,"arabic":"بِكَافٍ","translation":"যথেষ্ট","audioUrl":"wbw/039_036_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37742,"position":4,"arabic":"عَبْدَهُۥ ۖ","translation":"তাঁর দাসের (জন্যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/039_036_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37744,"position":5,"arabic":"وَيُخَوِّفُونَكَ","translation":"এবং তোমাকে  তারা ভয় দেখায়","audioUrl":"wbw/039_036_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37745,"position":6,"arabic":"بِٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"অন্যদের সম্পর্কে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_036_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37746,"position":7,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_036_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37747,"position":8,"arabic":"دُونِهِۦ ۚ","translation":"তিনি ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/039_036_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37749,"position":9,"arabic":"وَمَن","translation":"অথচ যাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_036_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37750,"position":10,"arabic":"يُضْلِلِ","translation":"পথভ্রষ্ট করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/039_036_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37751,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_036_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37752,"position":12,"arabic":"فَمَا","translation":"অতঃপর নেই","audioUrl":"wbw/039_036_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37753,"position":13,"arabic":"لَهُۥ","translation":"তার জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_036_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37754,"position":14,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"কোনো","audioUrl":"wbw/039_036_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37755,"position":15,"arabic":"هَادٍۢ","translation":"পথ প্রদর্শক","audioUrl":"wbw/039_036_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37756,"position":16,"arabic":"٣٦","translation":"(৩৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":37,"arabic":"وَمَن يَهْدِ ٱللَّهُ فَمَا لَهُۥ مِن مُّضِلٍّ ۗ أَلَيْسَ ٱللَّهُ بِعَزِيزٍۢ ذِى ٱنتِقَامٍۢ","translation":"whereas he whom God guides aright can never be led astray. Is not God almighty, an avenger of evil?","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4095.mp3","surahId":39,"words":[{"id":38598,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَن","translation":"এবং যাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_037_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38599,"position":2,"arabic":"يَهْدِ","translation":"পথ দেখান","audioUrl":"wbw/039_037_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38600,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_037_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38601,"position":4,"arabic":"فَمَا","translation":"তখন নেই","audioUrl":"wbw/039_037_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38602,"position":5,"arabic":"لَهُۥ","translation":"তার জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_037_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38603,"position":6,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"কোনো","audioUrl":"wbw/039_037_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38604,"position":7,"arabic":"مُّضِلٍّ ۗ","translation":"বিভ্রান্তকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/039_037_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38606,"position":8,"arabic":"أَلَيْسَ","translation":"নন কি","audioUrl":"wbw/039_037_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38607,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_037_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38608,"position":10,"arabic":"بِعَزِيزٍۢ","translation":"মহাপরাক্রমশালী","audioUrl":"wbw/039_037_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38609,"position":11,"arabic":"ذِى","translation":"আছে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_037_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38610,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱنتِقَامٍۢ","translation":"প্রতিশোধ গ্রহণকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/039_037_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38611,"position":13,"arabic":"٣٧","translation":"(৩৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":38,"arabic":"وَلَئِن سَأَلْتَهُم مَّنْ خَلَقَ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضَ لَيَقُولُنَّ ٱللَّهُ ۚ قُلْ أَفَرَءَيْتُم مَّا تَدْعُونَ مِن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ إِنْ أَرَادَنِىَ ٱللَّهُ بِضُرٍّ هَلْ هُنَّ كَٰشِفَٰتُ ضُرِّهِۦٓ أَوْ أَرَادَنِى بِرَحْمَةٍ هَلْ هُنَّ مُمْسِكَٰتُ رَحْمَتِهِۦ ۚ قُلْ حَسْبِىَ ٱللَّهُ ۖ عَلَيْهِ يَتَوَكَّلُ ٱلْمُتَوَكِّلُونَ","translation":"And thus it is [with most people]: if thou ask them, “Who is it that has created the heavens and the earth?” - they will surely answer, “God.” Say: “Have you, then, ever considered what it is that you invoke instead of God? If God wills that harm should befall me, could those [imaginary powers] remove the harm inflicted by Him? Or, if He wills that grace should alight on me, could they withhold His grace [from me]?” Say: “God is enough for me! In Him [alone] place their trust all who have trust [in His existence].”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4096.mp3","surahId":39,"words":[{"id":39476,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَئِن","translation":"এবং অবশ্যই যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/039_038_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39477,"position":2,"arabic":"سَأَلْتَهُم","translation":"তাদের তুমি প্রশ্ন করো","audioUrl":"wbw/039_038_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39478,"position":3,"arabic":"مَّنْ","translation":"কে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_038_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39479,"position":4,"arabic":"خَلَقَ","translation":"সৃষ্টি করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_038_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39480,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","translation":"আকাশকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_038_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39481,"position":6,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضَ","translation":"ও পৃথিবীকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_038_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39482,"position":7,"arabic":"لَيَقُولُنَّ","translation":"অবশ্যই  তারা বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_038_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39483,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ ۚ","translation":"\"আল্লাহ\"","audioUrl":"wbw/039_038_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3948